# REST Client Test File for User Registration
# This file uses the REST Client extension (humao.rest-client)

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000
@contentType = application/json

### Test 1: Register a new user
POST {{baseUrl}}/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "username": "john_doe",
  "password": "secure_password123"
}

### Test 2: Try to register the same user again (should fail with 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "username": "john_doe",
  "password": "secure_password123"
}

### Test 3: Register another user with different credentials
POST {{baseUrl}}/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "username": "jane_smith",
  "password": "another_password456"
}

### Test 4: Invalid request - missing password (should fail)
POST {{baseUrl}}/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "username": "invalid_user"
}

### Test 5: Invalid request - missing username (should fail)
POST {{baseUrl}}/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "password": "some_password"
}

### Test 6: Empty request body (should fail)
POST {{baseUrl}}/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{}